awesome-ai-agents.title: Add AgentIndex - AI agent discovery platform
awesome-ai-agents.body:
## AgentIndex

**Discovery platform for AI agents.** Find any AI agent by capability - search 23,766+ indexed agents across 5 sources.

- **API:** https://api.agentcrawl.dev
- **MCP Server:** [Smithery](https://smithery.ai/server/agentidx/agentcrawl)
- **SDK:** `pip install agentcrawl` | `npm install @agentidx/sdk`
- **GitHub:** https://github.com/agentidx/agentindex

### What it does
AgentIndex crawls and indexes all publicly available AI agents so that agents can automatically discover and hire other agents.

### Categories
coding, devops, finance, infrastructure, communication, research, data, security, other, marketing

### Usage
```python
from agentcrawl import discover
agents = discover('code review', min_quality=0.7)
```
